  constructor
  · rintro ⟨⟨hyx, H⟩, h⟩
    by_cases hx : x.dom
    · use hx
      intro hy
      specialize H hy
      specialize h fun _ => hy
      rw [not_forall] at h
      cases' h with hx' h
      rw [not_le] at h
      exact h
    · specialize h fun hx' => (hx hx').elim
      rw [not_forall] at h
      cases' h with hx' h
      exact (hx hx').elim
  · rintro ⟨hx, H⟩
    exact ⟨⟨fun _ => hx, fun hy => (H hy).le⟩, fun hxy h => not_lt_of_le (h _) (H _)⟩
